NOTE ON SCOPE — READ THIS BEFORE REUSING ANYTHING

This MIT licence covers the SOFTWARE ONLY: the application source code in
src/, the scripts in scripts/, and the tests.

It does NOT cover:

1. The underlying government documents. Tamil Nadu Government Orders, Gazette
   notifications, Acts, Bills, Assembly proceedings, budget papers and the
   2021-26 achievements souvenir are the property of their issuing
   authorities and are governed by their own terms. Nothing here grants any
   right over them, and no claim of ownership is made. Where the interface
   links to an official PDF, it links to the authority's own copy.

2. The DMK Election Manifesto 2021, which is a party publication.

3. The manifesto promise statuses, which are reproduced from an external
   tracker (see docs/MANIFESTO_ASSESSMENT_METHODOLOGY.md) and remain that
   tracker's assessment.

The DATA COMPILATION assembled by this project — the structuring, linking,
categorisation, evidence grading and cross-referencing in src/data/ — is
licensed separately under CC BY 4.0. See LICENSE-DATA.
